isii Agnes Taaka nke a makwaara dị ka Taaka Agnes Wejuli (amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 3 n'ọnwa Eprel n'afọ 1980) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Uganda, Social Worker, na onye omeiwu
Ọ bụ nwanyị nnọchi anya mpaghara nke Bugiri District
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ na nke itoolu, nke iri na nke iri na otu nke Uganda dị ka onye omeiwu

Ọ bụ onye otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị na-achị, National Resistance Movement. Ọ bụ nwanyị omebe iwu nke Bugiri District ugbu a n'oge(2021-2026) mgbe ekwupụtara ya dị ka onye mmeri na ntuli aka onye isi ala na nke ndị omebe iwu na Uganda.
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ Primary Leaving Examinations na Kigulu Girls Primary school na 1992 ma mesịa sonye na Bukoyo Senior Secondary School maka Uganda Certificate of Education na 1996
N'afọ 1999, Agnes sonyeere Iganga Senior Secondary School for Uganda Advanced Certificate of Education (UACE)
E nyere ya nzere bachelọ nke Arts na Social Science na Mahadum Makerere n'afọ 2004
Tụkwasị na nke a n'afọ 2007, ọ gara n'ihu n'agụmakwụkwọ ya ma nye ya asambodo na Iwu (Administrative Officers Law Course) site na Law Development Centre, Kampala.

N'agbata afọ 2006 na afọ 2014, Agnes rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye ọrụ mmepe obodo na Bugiri District Local Government ma mesịa bụrụ onye isi ọrụ mmepe ọha na eze na Bugiri Town Council ma rụọ ọrụ site na afọ 2014 ruo 2015
Site na 2010 ruo 2012, e mechara họpụta ya dị ka onye isi oche nke Bugiri District Local Government. Ọ na-eduzi Taaka Agnes Wejuli Development Foundation.

Site na afọ pụkụ abụọ na iri na ruo taa, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka nwanyị omebe iwu maka mpaghara Bugiri. N'oge ọ na-eje ozi dị ka onye omeiwu na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu nke Uganda, Agnes jere ozi ọzọ dị ka Kọmitii Ọrụ Ugbo

Ihe omume ntụrụndụ ya bụ Netball, na Dancing; ọ nwekwara mmasị pụrụ iche n'ịduzi ezinụlọ ndị ogbenye, otu obodo na ndị ntorobịa. Ọ sonyeere Uganda Women Parliamentary Association (UWOPA) na 10th parliament. Na Uganda Women Parliamentary Association (UWOPA), ọ na-eje ozi na kọmitii nke Iwu Ọrụ / Ikike Nkwado Akụ na ụba nke bụ mmekorita ya na Civil Society dị ka usoro maka iduzi nkwado na ntụziaka anọ dị mkpa.
